title: Claudia
description: In the Art Nouveau style known in Austria as Jugendstil, clusters of grapes with stylized leaves and tendrils within square frames, flanked horizontally by palmettes. Other stylized leaf forms become part of a symmetrical trellis-like design which is interspersed with daisies, leaves and tendrils. Background consists of stripes in light-to-dark arrangement of color, giving an ombre effect.
